#| msgctxt "promo/upgrade_to_full"
#| msgid ""
#| "Thank for playing Call to Arms. We hope you enjoyed the game so far!\n"
#| "\n"
#| "You can find some great upgrade options below. Enjoy more factions, singleplayer and cooperative support, Workshop content, custom editor battles and instant access to all factions!"
msgctxt "promo/upgrade_to_full"
msgid ""
"Thank you for playing Call to Arms. We hope you enjoyed the game so far!\n"
"\n"
"You can find some great upgrade options below. Enjoy more factions, singleplayer and cooperative support, Workshop content, custom editor battles and instant access to all factions!"
msgstr ""
"Gracias por jugar a Call to Arms. ¡Esperamos que te esté gustando!\n"
"\n"
"Aquí abajo encontrarás varias opciones de mejora. ¡Podrás jugar con más facciones, apoyo de un jugador y cooperativo, contenido de Steam Workshop, batallas personalizadas y tendrás acceso inmediato a todas las facciones!"

msgctxt "promo/upgrade_to_deluxe"
msgid ""
"Thank you for owning the Basic Edition of Call to Arms!\n"
"\n"
"You can upgrade your package to Deluxe Edition or Ultimate Edition and enjoy the game with even more content and extras!"
msgstr ""
"¡Gracias por elegir la Edición Básica de Call to Arms!\n"
"\n"
"¡Puedes actualizarla a la Edición Deluxe o Definitiva para contar con más contenido y extras!"

msgctxt "promo/upgrade_to_ultimate"
msgid ""
"Thank you for owning the Deluxe Edition of Call to Arms!\n"
"\n"
"Perhaps you want to upgrade your package with the Season Pass to Ultimate Edition and enjoy even more cooperative campaigns and early access to new factions!"
msgstr ""
"¡Gracias por elegir la Edición Deluxe de Call to Arms!\n"
"\n"
"Puedes adquirir cuando quieras el Season Pass y pasar a la Edición Definitiva, ¡tendrás acceso a más campañas en cooperativo y acceso anticipado a las nuevas facciones!"

msgctxt "announce_sale_text"
msgid ""
"Call to Arms is currently on Sale!\n"
"\n"
"Today you can upgrade your package at a great price.\n"
"Enjoy instant unit unlock, Singleplayer and Cooperative content, Workshop support and much more!"
msgstr ""
"¡Call to Arms está de rebajas!\n"
"\n"
"Aprovecha hoy y actualiza tu juego por un gran precio.\n"
"Desbloquea unidades al instante y disfruta de contenido de un jugador, cooperativo, de Steam Workshop y mucho más."

msgctxt "announce_sale_xmas_text"
msgid ""
"Happy Holidays!\n"
"\n"
"All Call to Arms upgrade packages and in-game items are currently on sale at a fantastic price. It's a perfect time to make yourself or friends a well deserved little present.\n"
"\n"
"Have fun and enjoy the time with your loved ones!"
msgstr ""
"¡Felices fiestas!\n"
"\n"
"Todos los packs de mejora y los objetos de Call to Arms están de rebajas. Es el momento perfecto para hacer un regalo a tus amigos... ¡o a ti!\n"
"\n"
"Diviértete y disfruta junto a tus seres queridos."

msgctxt "announce_discord"
msgid ""
"\n"
"\n"
"From Barbedwire Studios and Digitalmindsoft, \n"
"\n"
"We want to thank all the participants in the CtA - Gates of Hell: Ostfront beta test\n"
"\n"
" for all your feedback and the playtime invested.\n"
"\n"
"Join our Discord. Our goal is to build a strong community around our game\n"
"\n"
"See you in the battlefield, commanders!"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"\n"
"Desde Barbedwire Studios y Digitalmindsoft: \n"
"\n"
"Queremos agradeceros a todos los participantes de la beta de CtA - Gates of Hell: Ostfront\n"
"\n"
" el tiempo de juego invertido y vuestra opinión.\n"
"\n"
"Únete a nuestro Discord, queremos que el juego goce de una increíble comunidad\n"
"\n"
"¡Nos vemos en el campo de batalla, comandantes!"

msgctxt "announce_appeal"
msgid "DEAR PLAYERS!"
msgstr "¡JUGADORES!"

#| msgctxt "feedback_text"
#| msgid ""
#| "Dear Soldier,\n"
#| "\n"
#| "Thank you for your participation in Call to Arms. As a token of our gratitude for all of your contributions, we hereby award you the Bronze Star. Congratulations!\n"
#| "\n"
#| "As an independent developer studio, your opinion is what matters to us the most. In case you haven't done so yet, please consider leaving us a nice review. We want to hear your valuable feedback and thoughts on what you enjoy most about the game. Keep in mind, the more people who can find out about the game, the better we can make it for everyone.\n"
#| "\n"
#| "Thank you, and good luck on the battlefield!"
msgctxt "feedback_text"
msgid ""
"Dear Soldier,\n"
"\n"
"Thank you for your participation in Call to Arms. As a token of our gratitude for all of your contributions, we hereby award you the Bronze Star. Congratulations!\n"
"\n"
"As an independent developer studio, your opinion is what matters to us the most. In case you haven't done so yet, please consider leaving us a nice review. We want to hear your valuable feedback and thoughts on what you enjoy most about the game. Keep in mind, the more people who can find out about the game, the better we can make it for everyone.\n"
"\n"
"Thank you, and good luck on the battlefield!\n"
msgstr ""
"Atención, soldado:\n"
"\n"
"Te agradecemos tu participación en Call to Arms. Como muestra de gratitud por tus contribuciones, te hacemos entrega de la Estrella de bronce. Felicidades.\n"
"\n"
"Somos una desarrolladora independiente, por lo que tu opinión es lo que más nos importa. Nos gustaría pedirte que valores nuestro juego, si no lo has hecho ya. Queremos conocer tus comentarios y lo que más te ha gustado del juego. Cuanta más gente conozca nuestro juego, más podremos mejorarlo.\n"
"\n"
"Gracias, ¡y suerte en la batalla!\n"

#| msgctxt "feedback_text3"
#| msgid ""
#| "Dear Soldier,\n"
#| "\n"
#| "Thank you for your participation in Call to Arms. As a token of our gratitude for all of your contributions, we hereby award you the Gold Star. Congratulations!\n"
#| "\n"
#| "As an independent developer studio, your opinion is what matters to us the most. In case you haven't done so yet, please consider leaving us a nice review. We want to hear your valuable feedback and thoughts on what you enjoy most about the game. Keep in mind, the more people who can find out about the game, the better we can make it for everyone.\n"
#| "\n"
#| "Thank you, and good luck on the battlefield!"
msgctxt "feedback_text3"
msgid ""
"Dear Soldier,\n"
"\n"
"Thank you for your participation in Call to Arms. As a token of our gratitude for all of your contributions, we hereby award you the Gold Star. Congratulations!\n"
"\n"
"As an independent developer studio, your opinion is what matters to us the most. In case you haven't done so yet, please consider leaving us a nice review. We want to hear your valuable feedback and thoughts on what you enjoy most about the game. Keep in mind, the more people who can find out about the game, the better we can make it for everyone.\n"
"\n"
"Thank you, and good luck on the battlefield!\n"
msgstr ""
"Atención, soldado:\n"
"\n"
"Te agradecemos tu participación en Call to Arms. Como muestra de gratitud por tus contribuciones, te hacemos entrega de la Estrella de oro. Felicidades.\n"
"\n"
"Somos una desarrolladora independiente, por lo que tu opinión es lo que más nos importa. Nos gustaría pedirte que valores nuestro juego, si no lo has hecho ya. Queremos conocer tus comentarios y lo que más te ha gustado del juego. Cuanta más gente conozca nuestro juego, más podremos mejorarlo.\n"
"\n"
"Gracias, ¡y suerte en la batalla!\n"

